snippet.title: A Webbing Journey - Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
Play a cute little spider in this innovative and wholesome 3D puzzle platformer, where you explore lush and stunning islands to collect the most exotic flowers for your spider date.

Become a web designer, swing around, make new friends, and solve quests and mysterious puzzles during your journey.

This gameplay video is representing the current development stage of our game. Everything seen in it is subject to change.

Play the demo and wishlist our game on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2073910/A_Webbing_Journey/
